EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND.
DNC 19.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 0800Z TO 1900Z
   DAILY 28 NOV THRU 03 DEC IN AREA WITHIN
   32 MILES OF 57-20.9N 008-14.1W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD
   CONTACT HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON
   VHF CH 16 OR PHONE: 187 060 4449 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 032000Z DEC 17.
